Product name: 10 Vintage Austrian Pressed Glass Heart Beads / Vintage Austrian Pressed Glass Heart Beads // Vintage Picasso Pressed Glass Heart Beads
Description:
Size :: 10 mm
Qty :: 10 hearts
Circa :: 1960
Origin :: Austria
These beads are from around the 1960's. They are in beautiful condition, as they have never been used. 
They are a plum/violet purple mottled with a muted red/yellow terracotta and hints of reddish orange. The mottled color will not wash off or fade away. The process in making these beads was to use a gas to create the colors on the molten glass, this is why no two are ever alike in color, although the beads themselves are made in a mold so their size and shape will be identical, which is good for the artist looking for symmetry and consistency when making a line of jewelry

Product name: Male Dog Belly Band - Dogs w Bones n Fire Hydrants (#14)
Description:
This listing is for one belly band as pictured above. Belly bands are perfect for your male dog at home who marks, has incontinence problems, urinates when anxious, or to bring along when visiting friends or hotel stays for those dogs who like to mark new smells when they visit. These bands are designed to use with a urinary pad inside.
Each belly band is made with a top layer of 100% cotton, middle layer of fusible interfacing, and a bottom layer of soft fleece with a Velcro closure on the top of the band designed to allow for adjustment. All fabrics were rinsed in cold water and machine dried prior to cutting to avoid excessive shrinkage after construction.
I offer a wide variety of sizes increasing by 1 inch increments so you can easily pick a band size that will fit your dog just right. You will find the exact size selection above in the drop down box. 
When ordering the proper size band, measure the exact length of his waist where your boy's "business" is, being careful not to pull too tight. Select your size based on your dog's actual waist size. Example, a 14" waist should order the 13-15 band placing your dog's measurement in the middle of the size ordered. As the size increases, so does the width of the band as well as the amount Velcro that is used for the closure. Below you will find the approximate widths. 
8-11 Waist Bands are approximately 3.5" wide
12-15 Waist Bands are approximately 4" wide
16-19 Waist Bands are approximately 4.5" wide
20-23 Waist Bands are approximately 5" wide
24 plus Waist Bands are approximately 5.5" wide**
**If you are ordering a 24 plus sized band, please provide me with your dog's actual waist size in the comment section. 
PUL materials are available as an add-on which will be sewn into the band as a third layer in the middle of the band. You can find this upgrade in the "Waterproof PUL" section in my shop. This third layer also gives the bands more stability if you like a stiffer/thicker band. This is especially nice in the larger and wider sized bands.
Zorb materials are available as a washable pad that is used instead of a disposable pad or in the All-in-one Belly Band. They are listed in the "Zorb Products" Sections. All-in-one Belly bands use different materials which are designed to absorb urine into the band.

Product name: BEST SELLER!!! New Mini size! - UNPOPPABLE Ball - Dog Toy - Durable Dog Toys - Tough Dog Toys
Description:
These toys came from genuine desperation! We would constantly buy those 2 - 5 plastic balls at the grocery store on the way out so our fur babies could play with them for a few minutes & not even 30 seconds later the fun was over! But what a fun 30 seconds it would be! 
Then I had this brilliant idea! These balls are UNPOPPABLE! Just being crocheted, they never have a truly seamless surface. There are "holes" from stitch to stitch where those little teeth can slip right in without doing damage to the ball itself. 
You can even play tug of war with these without the ball falling apart! It will stretch out some and usually return to its original shape with a little help.
And if anything else It's just a great ball to kick around & has a good amount of bounce to it when you kick it up in the air.
*I wouldn't recommend these balls for heavy chewers. **This ball is not a chew toy!** My boy furbaby is obsessed with chewing things and he won't play fetch ever. He will sit down and chew on it if he can get it away from my girl furbaby. Over time chewing on it has frayed some strings but it still stays together. He also likes to pull the strings like he likes to pull with any small pieces or tags on toys. That's what will actually do damage to these balls. So if your dogs are like Bubba I wouldn't recommend these balls for you guys. 
These amazing Unpoppable balls come in 4 sizes!
Large -  is about the size of a Basketball. (30  4.00 extra s/h)
Medium -  is about the size of a melon. (20  0.85 extra for s/h)
Small - is a little bit bigger than a grapefruit.(Pictured in the first picture with littleblackfrenchie (10  normal shipping))
Mini - is about the size of a tennis ball. (Not pictured (6  normal shipping))
*These balls come in 1 solid color but I am more than happy to do multiple and custom colors.
*Do NOT leave animals unattended with these toys!
Care Instructions: Wash on gentle cycle with cool water & tumble dry with no heat.

Product name: Organic Coffee Scrub - Organic Body Scrub - Coffee Body Scrub -  4 oz Sugar Scrub- All Natural Sugar Scrub - Fair Trade Coffee  Sugar Scrub
Description:
Using Organic Coffee sugar scrub is like visiting the spa in your own shower! It gently rubs away dead skin cells, allowing your skin to feel rejuvenated. Sugar also naturally draws moisture to your skin to keep it hydrated--a good choice for your winter skin regimen! 
A 4 oz jar of Organic Coffee Sugar Scrub will keep your skin glowing and healthy! Coffee grounds can temporarily reduce the visibility of cellulite and make skin appear firmer. 
The scrub comes in an glass amber jar to preserve all the aromatherapy goodness of the essential oils! 
For easy scooping and to prevent water from entering the scrub (this is a preservative-free scrub!), add wooden bamboo spoon for 1. 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/271063984/bamboo-wooden-spoon-sugar-scrub-add-on?ref=shop_home_active_1
WHAT'S INSIDE:
Sweet Almond Oil- works as an emollient for softening and conditioning the skin. It's great for dry, problem skin. It's light and won't make your skin feel oily. 
Jojoba Oil- provides long-lasting moisture and resembles the skin's natural sebum, so it also won't leave your skin feeling oily or greasy. It's antimicrobial and anti-inflammatory so it may be ideal for those who suffer from acne. It is also balancing so it's ideal for all skin types. 
Organic Pure Cane Sugar- Sugar is a natural humectant, meaning it draws moisture from the air to the skin so it will help hydrate the skin. Sugar is also exfoliating so it will help rub off the dead skin cells to reveal the healthy newer skin below. 
Organic Fair-Trade Coffee Grounds- can temporarily reduce the visibility of cellulite and make skin appear firmer. 
We are proud to use locally-roasted Ricks Roasters Papua New Guinea Coffee. The coffee is naturally-grown on Papua New Guinea Highlands and is pesticide free! 
HOW TO USE: 
If the oils and sugar have separated a little, stir to remix. Take a dime-sized amount into your palm and rub in a circular motion on your body or your face. It will help to rub off the dead-skin cells while the oils will hydrate your skin. Rinse. It may seem like it's hard to wash off the oil, but don't worry! Your skin will soon soak it up and feel super soft and moisturized. This all-natural sugar scrub will make your skin so happy!
We also have a larger jar available. See 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/252299778/organic-coffee-scrub-fair-trade-coffee?ref=shop_home_active_5
Thanks for visiting our shop!!!

Product name: Natural Deodorant, Lavender Tea Tree, Sunny Citrus, Choose Your Scent, Aluminum Free, 2 ounce twist-up tube
Description:
*NEW* scents available - Serenity and Fresh Bamboo with baking soda!
For those sensitive to baking soda, all 3 scents are now available without baking soda.  Some people are sensitive to baking soda and may experience irritation from using such a deodorant.  If you experience any irritation when using this product, discontinue use immediately.  For the sake of my customers who have no issues with baking soda in this deodorant, I continue to offer the baking soda version as well.
I started using aluminum-free deodorants to avoid the irritating ingredients found in commercial antiperspirants and deodorants.  Finding the right deodorant wasn't easy, though.  I loved the idea of natural deodorants, but the ones in the stores just didn't work well for me.  And despite their "all natural" claims, the list of ingredients on the back didn't sound all that natural to me.
Natural deodorants won't stop perspiration, but rather use essential oils and other natural ingredients like baking soda, arrowroot and kaolin clay to absorb sweat and kill odor-causing bacteria.  
Note:  This product does not contain ingredients that prevent perspiration (your body's natural way of cooling you down and getting rid of toxins).  On very hot days, or depending on your activity level, you may need to re-apply.  Please allow your body time to adjust to natural products. 
Naturally anti-bacterial, anti-fungal and free of:
 - Aluminum
 - Parabens
 - Preservatives
 - Synthetic chemicals
 - Dyes
Lavender - 
Classic lavender floral scent available with or without baking soda

Product name: 3d Printed Fidget Spinner  - The Original Rounded Style
Description:
3d Printed Fidget Spinner - Rounded Style
These are 3d printed and assembled by hand. Tuned quality stainless steel bearing is inserted in the center and quality stainless steel bearings inserted as weights in the other holes. These spin for about 30 seconds once broken in.
Included:  (1) Tuned quality stainless steel center bearing
                   (2) 3 - Quality stainless steel counterweight bearings
                   (3) Caps for the middle ball bearing - These are user removable, see the FAQ below for additional info.
Optional: A Ceramic Center Bearing is now available as an upgrade! (This upgrade is ONLY the CENTER Bearing)
Frequently Asked Questions & Answers
1) Shipping times - Many customers ask about the related shipping time. We do our very best to keep on schedule with the estimated shipping time. Customers must understand these are handmade items, each one is printed, assembled, inspected, tested, and packaged. Job #1 is to ensure that the product is perfect when it leaves our hands, and all of this takes time. We feel that our spinners are well worth the wait. You will also see there are many instances where we ship well before the estimated shipping time. Furthermore, we are also at the mercy of other suppliers, for bearings and plastic. 
2) Spin Times - We do not guarantee spin time. We go through a long process of preparing the bearings, both stainless and ceramic, and have developed an awesome method of preparing and tuning the bearings for excellent spin times.  With that said, there are many factors involved that we cannot control, so there are no guarantees. We can honestly say that no two bearings are exactly the same, anyone who tells you that is not being honest. We have some ceramic bearings that we have prepared that spin for 3.5 minutes and some prepared the same exact way will get 1.5 minutes. Again, there is no guarantee on the spin time.
3) Caps - Currently the caps are being installed so that the customer can remove them. Permanent installation would mean that you could never clean the center bearing, change center caps, or re-use it in the event of the spinner being destroyed. We've decided to leave them removable. With that said, if your caps are not staying on, you can use a few methods to correct. a) Use super glue, but again, you will never get them off again, b) wrap a small piece of clear tape around the post. This is usually all that is needed to remedy the situation.
4) Returns: Returns will only be accepted if the item is damaged in the mail.  You must return the item to us, so that we can put the existing bearings into a new spinner body. Customer damaged returns will not be accepted. The customer must understand that these are plastic printed items, and therefore should understand that these are not indestructible. They must be handled with care.
5) Shipping Method - All items are shipped USPS First Class Mail with tracking in a bubble mailer. Our shipping cost is a flat 3 no matter how many items you order.

Product name: Art Deco Wedding Invitation. Great Gatsby Wedding Invitation
Description:
Art Deco / Great Gatsby Wedding Invitation Set - Unique, 100% hand drawn designs are featured on the front of these invitations. Inspired by the Fisher Building, Fox Theater, and Guardian Building of Detroit which encompass beautiful Art Deco architecture. These invitations are perfect for a Great Gatsby inspired or Art Deco themed wedding.
***********************************************************
ORDERING INSTRUCTIONS: Please use the drop-down menu next to "Invitation Type" to specify what set you would like: ***Please note all items below are for digital files that you can print yourself. If you would like me to provide printing, I would be more than happy to! Please send me a message for a quote.** 
INVITATION ONLY: Includes a 5 x 7" high quality PDF digital download, consisting of a front and back
INVITATION  RSVP: Includes the invitation above  5 x 3.5" RSVP card (front and back)
SET  DETAILS CARD: Includes the Invitation and RSVP Card above AND a 5 x 3.5" Details Card. 
SAVE-THE-DATE Matches the artwork on the RSVP's and are 5" x 3.5" - double sided 
THANK-YOU CARD: Standard folded size of 3.5" x 5" (2 per 8.5 x 11" sheet)
TOTAL SUITE - Includes the invitation, RSVP, Details card, Save the Date, and Thank-you cards. Substitutions may be made. Please inquire within.
SMALL SIGN: Artwork can be sized at 5 x 7" or 8 x 10" with the wording of your choice. Limit of 10 words.
LARGE SIGN: Artwork can be sized at 11" x 17", 18" x 24", or 24" x 36" with wording of your choice. Limit of 10 words
SEATING CHART: Artwork is 36" x 24" and can either be vertical or horizontal orientation orientation. This includes the couples' names, wedding date, and table numbers on the sign only. Adding names would be an additional fee at my hourly rate of 50 per hour.  I can copy your list from a word doc.
Upon approval of the design, each file will be emailed to you in *PDF form (and will include .125 bleeds on each file) to be printed at your favorite local printer. I suggest using a privately owned print shop and not a chain. From my experience, I find privately owned print shops deliver higher quality prints and are usually much more affordable.
*Please be aware that I only send invitations in PDF form as this ensures the highest quality invitations and that your text is the most crisp. JPEG files are for photos only - text does not print well on JPEG files.
HOW IT WORKS:
STEP 1: After you have purchased your desired invitation set, please send me your wedding information. You can send the information in the notes section during purchase, as an Etsy conversation, or as an email to gingersnapgraphics [!at] gmail.com
Please make sure to provide:
FOR INVITATIONS:
1. Name of couple that is to be married (written exactly as you want it to appear)
2. Names of Parents (ONLY if you want them included in the wording
3. Date and Time of Wedding
4. Wedding Ceremony Name and Address
5. If you want, Reception to Follow on there...please let me know.
FOR RSVP CARDS:
1. Meal Options (if any)
2. RSVP by: Date 
3. Any wording that you would like changed, please send as well.
FOR DETAILS CARDS:
1. Wedding Ceremony Location/Address
2. Reception Location / Address (if different from ceremony site) 
3. Accommodations: Hotel name/Address, Group rate information, deadline to reserve 
4. Wedding Website URL (if necessary)
STEP 2: In two business days or less, I will send you your first proof. This means I will send a copy of the invitation (and other cards) containing the information as you have given it to me to your e-mail
STEP 3: YOU send me a message approving the proof or requesting additional changes. Please note that this purchase includes a total of 3 revisions.
STEP 4: Upon Approval of your finished design, I will e-mail you the final digital invitation set in three separate files so you can take them in for printing at your favorite local printer.
INTERESTED IN ME HANDLING PRINTING???
******************************************************************
If you would rather have me print these invites and ship them to you, rather than deal with the hassle of finding a good printer, No Problem! Just purchase this listing along with the "100 Printing Deposit" listed in my Etsy Store. All invitations are printed on 120 lb. matte card stock. A complete list of my printing fees for invitations is listed in the "Printing Deposit" Listing. The 100 deposit will go directly towards your printing costs.
OTHER STUFF YOU SHOULD KNOW:
Please note that there may be some slight color variations due to differences in computer monitors. 
Please review your proof carefully. Should you find an error after the final invitation has been made I am happy to fix it for you, however, I cannot refund your printing expenses.
OF LEGAL IMPORTANCE:
Please respect my work and do not copy it without my permission. This is a no-no!

## We offer this fabric by the 1/2 yard. To order 1 yard, select a quantity of 2 and so on. I will cut your fabric in one continuous piece.
## Please visit www.spindleandrose.com for free shipping on US orders of 50 or more AND to find additional cuts of fabric including 1/4 yard, 1/2 yard, 3/4 yard, 1 yard, and Fat Quarters!
## Find this product with all of the options described above at:
www.spindleandrose.com/products/whale-fabric-charley-harper-fabric-birch-organic-fabrics-ocean-fabric-humpback-whale-print-whales-breaching-beach-decor-sea
 
"Love on the Richter Scale"
100% Certified organic cotton from Birch Fabrics. Designed by Charley Harper from his Maritime Collection.
Wow... Humpbacks rise to meet one another like seismic waves – a love so strong as to cross oceans, cause the earth to shake.
Whales are about five and a quarter inches tall.
Long distance is the next best thing to being there. But a dove in love would rather reach out and touch someone. Spring is in the air and all lines are busy with local calls as the wooing and cooing commences. Charley Harper
 
*Care Instructions: Birch Fabrics recommends washing their fabric on the gentle cycle in cold water with like colors using a fragrance free, non-chlorinated detergent that is preferably, environmentally friendly. You can dry your fabric on low, but hang drying will further increase the fabric's longevity. ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
*Multiple lengths of the same fabric will be cut as one continuous piece*
SHIPPING POLICIES:
I will refund any significant (1 and over) shipping overages ~ I can typically fit up to 2 and 1/2 yards of fabric in a First Class Package for under 4, however, certain types of fabric are heavier so there are exceptions. More than 2 1/2 yards of material makes the weight of the package too heavy for First Class and will ship Priority but I will choose the best Flat Rate Priority option to ship your fabric and refund any overages. For example, I can typically fit 2-3 yards in a flat rate legal envelope for 6.95 (Canvas, Knit, and Double Gauze may be too thick) and 5-8 yards depending on the fabric in a Flat Rate Padded Envelope for 7.20. Larger orders may need to go in a medium flat rate box. Again, it depends on the weight and thickness of the fabric but I will choose the least expensive option and refund overages.
***FREE SHIPPING on orders over 50 if you order on the website spindleandrose.com*****
INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING
I am happy and honored to have international orders!! Please note that 98% of my international packages have arrived successfully by First Class International Package to the destination within 2-3 weeks. I do understand it is expensive to ship and First Class International is the most affordable option, however please note that First Class International is NOT TRACKABLE. A tracking number is provided and in most cases we can follow that number along with the package on its route to you, but if there are ANY issues, the US post office WILL NOT HELP ME track down your package.
If you are concerned about your order, please contact me. I am more than happy to see what I can do to fix the situation and make this a pleasant experience :) Just please understand, once the fabric is delivered to the post office, if it is First Class International Package, it is out of my hands. Priority International is the only guaranteed tracking that includes any help from post office personnel, but I completely understand that it is an expensive shipping option. IF SOMETHING IS NOT RIGHT
I check and double check your order because I know how exciting it is to get new material for awaiting projects! Of course, if I make any mistakes and your order is not correct, I will do all I can to make it right!
I want my customers to get the newest, quality fabric from my shop, so typically, unless it is my mistake, I can't accept returns on cut fabric. However, my main priority is making my customers happy, so, if there's a concern, let's talk about it and see what I can do!
Thank you so much for visiting! 
Warmest Regards,
<3 Alexa

Description:
Ecru/Undyed/Natural Corriedale wool roving (combed top), spinning fiber - 4 ounces **
This is a beautiful, naturally colored wool that I use as the base for some of the lovely colorways you see here! Sheepish Creations is now offering this lovely wool with the discount that comes with buying in bulk!
For those of you who enjoy spinning, here's 100% lovely Corriedale fiber. This is soft, lofty, and has a long staple so it's fabulous for all skill levels. This is processed as combed top, although is often incorrectly referred to as roving. I spin this fiber myself, and I love the lofty and unique yarn that I can achieve so easily.
Have fun trying out a less-common type of wool. Sure to be a pleasure to spin!
This wool is also perfect for stuffing waldorf dolls!
This roving is professionally processed, free of neps, felting, and general ickiness. As you can tell from the picture, it is a lovely natural shade.
